channel.title: Augustus - Veni Vidi Vici
channel.description:
[font=georgia][size=18pt][CENTER] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/YKLMp.png[/img] I released this a long time on Rune-Server. I thought, Why shouldn't I released this on MPSC. So here it is. I only want to release the first version of Augustus before I move on to the next Augustus's updates with Jacob` on R-S.
[url=http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-server/projects/463345-augustus-veni-vidi-vici-working-new-combat-concept.html]Project thread[/url]
[url=http://www.mediafire.com/?2v4tx2bby7a1p0x]Download - Mediafire[/url] [url=http://depositfiles.com/files/wapw5b15d]Download - DepositFiles[/url] [url=http://www.multiupload.nl/P89XU06UV5]Download - MultiUpload[/url] [url=http://www.putlocker.com/file/34ADAA3B5BF5D08F]Download - PutLocker[/url] [url=http://up.ht/12ZapMU]Download - Uppit[/url]
Also, yes I know, I said it won't get released in my project thread.. But I changed my mind. I'll only release the first version of it so you can rip anything you want.
[hr][hr]
[b]Removing / Enabling the unfinished animated background:[/b] The animated background isn't done. You can switch it with the boolean. You can disable it by searching [CODE]drawAnimatedWorldBackground(true);[/CODE] in Client.java and changing the true to false.
[hr][hr]
[b]Client [Fixes]:[/b] 1- 'Stove, Firecape & Green tree fix: Download: [url=http://up.ht/12Zaznx]Models[/url] Info: Repack those models with Rs cache suite.
If you find any other bugs/problems, tell me.
[b]Server[Fixes]:[/b] 1- Delete the current src folder. Download this: [url=http://up.ht/12ZdNY2]src[/url] or [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?w66ca412yxs0ht7]src[/url] And put the src folder to your server folder.
[hr][hr]
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/tBzaF.png[/img]
[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5DTNnjhs5p8]Augustus's Login/Lobby - YouTube[/url]
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/zs1Xr.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/eeFxd.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/HSkOB.png[/img]
[hr]
*I'm Compass_ on R-S. [/CENTER][/size][/font]
